name: Discount Grocery Store
overview: DiscountGroceries.com delivers to you thousands of food and grocery items with just a click of your mouse button. You can find everything you need to prepare your family’s meals from soups and appetizers, main dishes to desserts and snacks. We also have household supplies, pet supplies and health products that you would have to look for in specialty shops. Nothing but the best quality grocery items at the lowest prices. All you could possibly need at home are available right here at DiscountGroceries.com. Store owner, Joe Carcione, is a proud father of two and the owner of DiscountGroceries.com. He lives together with his wife, Amy, and their twin daughters, Chloe and Jenna. They have 2 dogs, a Pomeranian named Ginger and a cute Pug named Pugzilla. Joe enjoys spending quality time with his family and loves cooking for them every weekends. His specialty is lasagna, which are his daughters’ favorites.
